Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.38,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.38,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.44,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.44,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:33.65,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:33.65,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:56.43,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:56.43,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:07.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:07.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:36.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)\move(632,119,627,126)\frz-1\fscy90\be1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\bord0.1\shad0\fs42\t(0,4114,\fs40)\c&H8D9ED9&\3c&HAFE4E2&}8{\c&H7F908C&} more days until{\c&H8C956A&} the Hamabi Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:41.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Melt the wax from inside with the torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It cracked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:51.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, how in the world should I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:04.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping the strength and speed the\Nsame, slide it down slowly like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:08.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The monthly magazine "The Handbook of Art"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's a special edition on school festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been asked to include your work\Nin it again this year, Hanamoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean you should feel pressured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:22.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax and do what you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:26.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Just as you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:27.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:33.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I just have to do it like I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:37.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time... Just like always... Just like always...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll take the trash out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:44.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll wash all the washrags, so please\Nthrow them all in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:47.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you, Yamada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:55.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As to be expected during the school\Nfestival — everyone's working late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:02.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst the faint scent of the fragrant\Nolives, an orange flame lights up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already the fifth time I'm seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:13.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Until last year, he was somewhere around these lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:16.25,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Hamabi Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:19.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would make errands for myself and repeatedly\Nwalk by places where I might see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to see a little bit of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped to just hear his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hagu-chan here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamada. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought I'd visit before the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Ayu! Roll cakes and steamed bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The chocolate one is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two, don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You glutton!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just gloomily doodling until a second ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.30,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-25\shad0\bord1\be1\fs46\b0\fscy80\fscx85\fnAlsina Ultrajada\pos(464,238)\c&H91999E&\3c&HE4EBF1&}I want a broach of a little bird
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.30,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz3\shad0\bord0\fs46\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\pos(358,339)\c&H91999E&}Like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were! Your work hasn't been progressing at all lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your usual pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! An opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My roll cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san, may I open this bag of steamed bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that they haven't eaten dinner yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,9:55 PM... We'll barely make it for Kinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You have a minute to decide. My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.53,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\bord1.7\be1\shad0\fs28\3c&HDEEDF0&\c&H757A7C&}Chinese Food Delivery\NOshinagaki\N{\c&H8188B2&}Kinka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a working man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still open? Can I place an order for delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I want miso ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:39.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want roast pork ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a fu rong bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I want Japanese-style fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.97,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I should also say it like everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I love you! I love you!\NOkay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:55.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I am, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fine, I told you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.60,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about it too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.90,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Just casually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.74,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.12,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is saying it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.95,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.00,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:18.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There... you... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada... Hey, Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.55,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayama's so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.77,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,H-His voice... His hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san! Morita-san ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My roll cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Eat slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the key to the material room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san left something so important here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return it on my way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:01.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go get some scrap wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal, Mayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating so slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.06,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Right to left: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Work Room (1), Material Room, Storage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, how's your work coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just needed to do it like I always do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I need to get to work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:56.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to steal back the roll cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bite, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't listen to what others say, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for, Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A block of wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:23.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:28.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One that's hard, dry, and white-ish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there are also some over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:39.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:04.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to work hard, just like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:16.35,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Tea cup: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Hanamoto Hagumi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:24.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:30.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.30,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.22,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:59.19,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.90,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I not telling her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.03,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have told her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:05.86,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.36,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.88,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That "it might be from Morita-san"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:34.31,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Or that "he might like you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're napping in a place like this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are leaves piling up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if you catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:55.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:02.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:13.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The October breeze was cold, and the rays of\Nthe low afternoon sun were bright white.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The world, as if stopped, was stained a silver hue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:23.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamily wondered if the lunar surface\Nlooked something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:30.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wondered so... dreamily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No Christmas party this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking forward to it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:47.46,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Back of the jackets: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Hamadayama Central Avenue\NShopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to help out at my family's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:52.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, our shopping district is going\Nthrough a tough time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:56.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A big supermarket opened on the other\Nside of the train station, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\bord2\shad0\fs56\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\pos(445,41)\3c&H2A3F30&\c&H2CE1EA&}Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.47,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\bord1.6\be1\shad0\frz9\fs56\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\move(285,296,285,329)\c&H374B58&\3c&HD5DFDC&}run-down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:56.68,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\bord2\shad0\fs56\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\pos(445,41)\c&H4B5EE6&\3c&H2A3F30&}Shuei
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:56.68,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\bord0.5\be1\shad0\frz-35\fs56\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\move(782,60,782,110)\3c&H464F57&\c&H7872B1&}sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:03.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end for a small shopping district\Nlike ours if we lose out on spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This Christmas, I'm going to put in a lot\Nspirit and liven up our shopping district!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:09.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The Christmas party...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:31.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san! You ate the snacks we bought, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:31.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\shad0\bord0\b0\fs18\c&H7F8B8F&\pos(436,335)}bill
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You better pay us back for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:35.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! This is the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't pay with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A grappling hook...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The "nin" in "Shinobu" is the "nin" in "ninja"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.06,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&}Shinobu's name ({\be1\3c&H635514&}忍{\be0\3c&H000000&}) is the first kanji of "{\be1\3c&H635514&}ninja{\be1\3c&H000000&}" ({\be0\3c&H635514&}忍者{\be1\3c&H000000&}).
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back our snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or pay for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:12:00.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan has a slight idea of who gave her the broach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:07.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I, unable to give her the answer, didn't mention Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:14.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That broach with the little bird is perched on her\Nfavorite bag with the blue sky design.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayu, until when will you be helping out at the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:23.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be from the 22nd to the 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:27.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also be working delivering year-end gifts around that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Hagu-chan, do you want to work with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be selling Christmas cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Working, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd like to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:43.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can dress up like Santa, and we'll be able to get all the\Nleftover cakes and roasted chicken on Christmas day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.25,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\be1\shad0\4c&H4B87B4&\fs29\move(409,295,409,0)\fnArial\3c&H6F6F6F&\c&H4B79D8&}Central Avenue Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:55.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, she doesn't look like a Santa.\NWhy does she look more like a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:13:00.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second. Didn't we have a kid's\Ncostume or something smaller?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously in college?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:06.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First, try saying "Welcome."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}W-Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:13.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Haven't you worked before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of those caged-up kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:18.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean boxed-up, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:23.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that her image overlapped with\Nour Little Ham that died two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Ham?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name of the hamster we used to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A hamster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We're selling them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:38.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Hanamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:46.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs27\fscy90\3c&HACE5F0&\c&H6597AE&\pos(232,55)}Bakery {\fs32\c&H75A090&}Matsumoto
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:46.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\frz-89\fnArial Narrow\fs15\c&H667279&\pos(529,405)}Whipped Cream
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:46.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\frz-88\fnArial Narrow\fs15\c&H667279&\pos(582,401)}Chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:46.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\frz-90\fnArial Narrow\fs15\c&H667279&\pos(708,393)}Marron
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:41.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you during the christmas sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ippei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The cakes Ippei-san makes are really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's work hard to sell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:51.02,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs36\frz1\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\c&H7EAD9B&\pos(167,150)}Big Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:51.02,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs36\frz1\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\c&H7EAD9B&\pos(180,228)}Sale
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:51.02,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord1\fscx80\fad(50,0)\fs13\pos(420,239)\3c&H6F808C&\c&H9BBADA&}bread & cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:55.28,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs26\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\pos(441,244)\c&H5F93BD&\frz332.856\frx6\fry29}Hamadayama Central Avenue\NShopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Five whipped cream cakes. Just a second, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, eight of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:58.74,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs27\fscy90\3c&HACE5F0&\c&H6597AE&\pos(232,55)}Bakery {\fs32\c&H75A090&}Matsumoto
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Five whipped cream! Three chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Hagu-chan, that's a marron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get a large bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-san, your voice is too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:08.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, can you get four rolls of 100 yen coins in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:12.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the five ice cream cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:13.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the change yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:21.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's your first time at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm being very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:33.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is that you calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:37.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you need to say "Welcome!" and "Thank you!" much louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:43.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it hasn't been that busy today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, there aren't a lot of customers this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:50.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We usually sell half the cakes by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The supermarket is completely beating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:00.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, not only this store, but the\Nother ones will also be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:05.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ippei-san, we, the third generation,\Nneed to do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gather all the third generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:15.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no time or money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:18.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we need to make something to attract customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but the only things we might be able to use are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:24.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the old cotton candy machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this big pot for making sweet sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:32.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ayu. I wasn't helpful at all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:36.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. You were convincingly useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Ippei-san! Today was only her first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:42.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll get the hang of things tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:48.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But only cotton candy and sweet sake is a little plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The supermarket is very nicely decorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:53.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:54.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but for us to do something by tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:57.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:05.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:06.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:09.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is there a bicycle shop around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:21.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:30.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be passing out cotton candy and sweet sake at 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come with your mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:41.73,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H64&\3a&H64&\frz4\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs43\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\i1\3c&HBCDCE9&\pos(349,60)\c&H9699CB&\frx10\fry5}Yamada Liquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dad... and everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for doing this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you make that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Hagu-chan's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:53.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it out of the balloons we had in storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposedly called "balloon art."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:58.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Little Ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Ham?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:03.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, since it's about time for me to go to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:04.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:05.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:09.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is so bright, my eyeballs feel like they're gonna explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:13.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for helping out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:17.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't have been able to finish\Nit if you hadn't come, Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:18.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As to be expected from the Hagu-master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:19.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you understand her instructions so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:26.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea what Hanamoto-san was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:34.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you squeeze this and that together and\Ntwist it around like so to make it pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you squeeze it some more and twist them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:35.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:42.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be delivering the Hamadayama District today,\Nso I'll pass by on my bicycle a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll wave to you, then, so look out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:55.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to not like Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wave to you if I see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:04.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart ached every time I saw the colorful illumination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:11.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like I was being asked, "Are you happy\Nright now?" or "Is there a place for you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.62,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, please help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:45.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in this glittering December city, I didn't feel lonely even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:54.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, I went to my first job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are my wage and cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:58.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\be1\shad0\b0\fs33\pos(427,152)\3c&H516F8A&\c&H2C3B45&}Wage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please eat it, Shuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Namu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:03.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're telling you, Hagu-chan! This is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:09.92,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Package: {\be1\3c&H000000&}sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy's all worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were working all throughout the break, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:19.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've put up enough Christmas decorations\Nat work to last me a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:24.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you said that you might have some\Nwork-related parties to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:32.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell us that it's a work-related party, but you actually\Ntook a present to that apartment you stalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:37.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you saw that the lights were out, became\Ndisappointed, and dejectedly came our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about what happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:42.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mouth... I'll shut it up for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:44.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\frz-73\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs29\move(602,220,848,220)\3c&HCCDFE0&\c&H7773A1&}Right on the Spot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, such pretty flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:50.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can see a big river.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:52.84,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\3c&H000000&}He is referring to {\be0\3c&H635514&}the Sanzu no Kawa {\be1\3c&H000000&}(the River Styx).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, you can't cross that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Mayama. There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:12.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:16.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That broach...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who made that broach is probably Mo—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:20.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo People!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:23.25,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Momo: {\be1\3c&H000000&}"peach" in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:23.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-Wha-What is it all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no deep meaning to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:31.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, do you want some green\Ntea, black tea, or maybe coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coffee, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll help out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat the cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:48.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:58.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I abruptly realized that this was the last\NChristmas that we'd get to quietly spend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:01.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's yours, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I keep blinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:14.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like snapping the shutter of a camera, wishing to\Nimprint this moment somewhere in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:18.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst the sweet scent of the cake and everyone's laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.94,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.94,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:33.07,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:33.07,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.20,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.20,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.29,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.29,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:50.04,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:50.04,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.13,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.13,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.51,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.51,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:06.43,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:06.43,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:12.65,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:12.65,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:18.86,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:18.86,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:24.99,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:24.99,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:34.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: We fly across the sky.
